        <div class="msgSubject">thoughts on heroics?</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-09-22 13:49:36   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-128518497616643769" id="quote-128518497616643769" class="msgQuoteCheck"/><label for="quote-128518497616643769"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=21&amp;mid=128518497616643769&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=128518497616643769&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow" onclick="return multiQuote(this)">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_128518497616643769" onclick="followToggle('add','128518497616643769')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
