      <div class="msgContentFrame">So, the heroics are now available on the beta.  I'm not in the beta, but I am curious.  Blizz has talked about wanting to go back to more of a TBC level of difficulty...did they deliver (assuming it isn't all nerfed to hell), or is this just WOTLK 2.0?  Anyone in the beta want to give some feedback?  This is something probably a lot of PVE players have really wanted to know...will there actually be a challenge?<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>Behold the power of procrasti</div></div>
      <div class="msgFtFrame"><div class="msgFtFrameFix"></div><div class="msgReplies"><a href="javascript:scrollTo(0,0);">&#9650; Page top</a> |   <a href="/forum.html?forum=21&amp;mid=128518497616643769&amp;page=1&amp;howmany=50#msg128518497616643769" class="icon-linktothis" rel="nofollow">Link to this post</a>  57 replies</div>Posting from The red moon</div>
