ave any patience and don't give a damn that they're doing 2k dps in ICC.  I think that if you have really epic gear, you should have to do something that's at least kind of epic.  :)  (laughing at myself right now for using the word &quot;epic&quot; this many times today) <br /> <br />edited to add: Yeah, I wish they didn't take attunements out, too.  I was excited when I got to the point of having to earn my keys and such, and was so happy when I could get into Kara on my own!  Maybe they could make it a little less grindy, but I think it helped keep lazy douchebags out of dungeons they didn't belong in.  :) <br /> <br />/rant <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Sep 23rd 2010  8:14pm by Trilliandent </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>&quot;could u guys pls tell me how to do herbalism on dead monster?&quot;</div></div>
