      <div class="msgContentFrame">I imagine they will start out difficult but like WOTLK later on as people start getting better and better gear they will end up being fairly simple.  I see some people not happy with the 15 min heroic runs but really as the game is designed right now how else does a lvl 80 gear up to raid?  You either have to drop a ton of gold on BOE AH gear (which is foolish this close to an expansion), or mass run heroics and get t9/t10 gear.  People don't raid low end raid zones anymore unless they are trying for hardmode achievements, and thanks to GS if you don't have 400 more GS than actually required for a raid zone you can't get in anyways. <br /> <br />Im all for interesting boss encounters, but I don't want to see something so difficult that I will be scared to join random PUG's.  I don't care to wipe while raiding, but expensive repairbills to get through a heroic are just a waste.  I still don't think there was anything wrong with WOTLK heroic difficulty just now everyone is over geared for them now.  </div>
