      <div class="msgContentFrame">I tried some heroics again last night (new patch) as a DK tank.  VC went WONDERFULLY until the third boss. <br />Trash pulls require CC on certain pulls now, but not a lot.  Target selection is NECESSARY as the healer won't be able to keep up with the strongets mobs hitting a 333 geared tank for more than a few dozen hits. <br />Threat isn't the hair pulling issue it was near the beginning of the beta.  Blizzard removed threat decay, which was annoying and unneccessary.  That's a lot of letters. <br />In short, the dungeon was difficult but fun, the balance that should be struck.  There were wipes, around 20 of them, before the group finally fell apart at the third boss, who just kept CRUSHING us.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>Druid-Wakayaja||Paladin-Zavo||Warrior-Drest||Mage-Versi||Shaman-Kuroderm||Hunter-Fiagai||Death Knight-Zavoyevatd|| <br />^Sisters of Elune^ <br />Rogue-Nalgas||Priest-Sacerdot|| <br />^Cenarian Circle^ <br />1983 Mazda RX7 GSL - Rexie - My Garage <br /> <br />&quot;Saying that a druid can go resto and do well in arena and saying that a hunter can't do the same doesn't make any sense whatsoever.&quot; - Wait. . . what?</div></div>
